data.description: 2023 roof, 2016 AC unit, plumbing 2016, privacy fence 2016. Great floorplan with a big living room, open concept kitchen with plenty cabinet room with granite countertop and splash installed. House has lots of light from the sliding doors that lead out to the lanai and outdoor patio, which is all ready to host BBQ and entertain guests.  Great location to skip traffic when going or coming from work!
